{"tid":474424,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"分享下有咩連載緊嘅輕小說好睇！！！！！","createTime":"2017-11-20T06:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T14:47:33.000Z","uid":98507,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"2695a0e88e9bb4bc16592ae3ccec3f283769177b","tid":474424,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:52:49.000Z","msg":"盡量分享下未有動畫化嗰啲<br />\n磚：<br />\n青春豬頭系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同櫻花莊同一作者<br />\n講青春期嘅少男少女會因為各種不安同煩惱而引起各種超自然現象<br />\n然後男主就呢班<del>少男</del>少女解決問題<br />\n個人認為係近年黎最出色嘅輕小說之一<br />\n文筆唔多講有睇櫻花莊都知唔會差<br />\n對比起櫻花莊嘅男主 今次嘅男主顯得成熟更多 唔會睇到拳頭硬<br />\n友情愛情親情基本三大元素都有齊<br />\n濃濃閃光彈之中又有虐心同感動<br />\n尤其係五六七卷嘅兩個只能活一個選擇題<br />\n睇到我仲糾結過男主<br />\n好耐未試過睇到個心咁有起伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未睇過嘅睇下 唔好睇可以返黎打柒我<br />\n<br />\nbtw m男一定要睇"},{"pid":"b610cef81846fad4b7c588226e986960d13bcab6","tid":474424,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:04:02.000Z","msg":"樓主sick野<br />\n呢個男主討好到不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5cf1b80f5dc8b769ca9041d8d4de1e8183a74d","tid":474424,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:04:52.000Z","msg":"仲以為成句都係個書名<br />\nbtw有無付費app係快又齊"},{"pid":"758dc6c9b8d5ca68fe0e7a7e4f0b52b93a605a15","tid":474424,"uid":137551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:20:02.000Z","msg":"鴨志田一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252db8b2c968a3f07aea42f7862a494a4a92b5bc","tid":474424,"uid":39020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef6c0780c4bc0a